Fy_mooninite README
made by: kaos4u
date: 4/18/07
contact info: kaos4u2004@yahoo.com
solidsurf.info
filesize: 4.82 MB
unzip to this path:
C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\Your Account Name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

==================================

This map was created in honor of Aqua Teen Hunger Force, and the best 2-D charactures ever created "The Mooninites".

This is a fight yard style map.  Every player spawns with a scout, deagle, knife, and a nade.  Also, there is buyzones in the very middle of the map.  This map has a secret hidden button that changes the gravity for 30 seconds.

==================================

Special thanks to Very_Angry_Beaver the creator of AB_space skybox textures, and SintaxError for finding it for me long after the site that hosted it went down.  Also thanks to everyone at the Williams Street, for making some of the best cartoons ever.

Custom moon textures made by me kaos4u.
